{"word":"G1460 - ἐγκατοικέω - enkatoikéō - eng-kat-oy-keh'-o - Dwell among","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐγκατοικέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enkatoikéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">eng-kat-oy-keh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dwell among</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வாசமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to dwell among"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G2730 - κατοικέω - katoikéō - kat-oy-keh'-o/2730\">G2730</a>; to <i>settle down in</i> a place, that is, <i>reside:</i> - dwell among.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}